high_descs: Turn around, go straight to the counter, turn right and go to the coffee maker.
Take the mug that is on the coffee maker.
Turn left, go to the oven, then look at the microwave above the oven.
Put the mug in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the mug out of the microwave.
Turn around, go to the right to the brown shelves across the room.
Put the mug on the right side of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk then walk left to the coffee machine.
Grab the cup from the coffee machine.
Turn left then walk to face the stove.
Warm the cup up for 3 seconds in the microwave above the stove.
Turn around and head right to the shelves.
Place the cup on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed up cup on the top shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the end of the kitchen counter then turn left and move to the dishwasher next to the sink.
Remove the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn left, move towards the oven, then turn right and face the microwave above the oven.
Place the mug in the microwave, heat it using the microwave, then take the mug out of the microwave and close the microwave door.

Turn left and move towards the wall past the oven then turn left and move towards the refrigerator, then turn right and move towards the door, and turn left and move to the shelves in the corner of the room.
Place the mug on the shelves' top shelf to the right of the red vase.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on a shelf.
